# Debugging and Configuration for Apache in Docker Container

## Accessing the Docker Container
- Command: `docker exec -it [container_id] bash`

## Checking Apache Status
- Check Status: `service apache2 status`
- Start Apache: `service apache2 start`

## Configuring Apache
- Navigate to Document Root: `cd /var/www/html`
- Edit or Create index.html: `vi index.html`
- Add the following content to index.html: `Hello Holberton`

## Restarting Apache
- Command: `service apache2 restart`

## Exiting the Container
- Command: `exit`
